title: 09/07/21 DPS Hour 1 College Football Talk
itunes:title: 09/07/21 DPS Hour 1 College Football Talk
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan and company discuss the most eye-popping outcomes from college football's first full week, as well as the redemption stories of a handful of college coaches. Also, Dan is confused by targeting rules that continue to impact the college game well beyond the play in question.
